      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Thermostats and fridges operate independently, so there is no built-in sensor sync that would trigger a simultaneous temperature drop and compressor activation. Instantaneous changes in two separate smart home devices usually indicate either a fake power outage resetting timers, an automated energy-saving mode masquerading as a device feature, or simply your heightened awareness during stressful moments. For a complete explanation or to reset these devices, please contact your specific smart home device support team or verify your home automation app settings.",
