      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i checked the logs and they both ping the same cloud server at the exact same time whenever it happens. if it was just my \"conditioned expectation,\" why would there be a spike in network traffic? i feel like i'm being watched or monitored by the hardware itself. how would someone even go about seeing if there's hidden data being sent between them or to a third party? like, is there a way to check if the firmware is actually running extra processes in the background?",
