      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "While devices can technically connect to the same cloud server simultaneously, this does not automatically indicate they are communicating unpublished data or listening for specific audio cues. Verifying hidden processes or firmware behavior is generally outside the scope of standard user diagnostics without manufacturer tools, as smart home appliances do not typically provide transparent logic logs to their owners. Given the absence of public evidence for such advanced audio-emotion analysis in consumer electronics, it remains highly unlikely that your hardware is actively monitoring your mood to control appliances.",
